data.title: South Staffordshire District Council
data.meta_description: There are 27 parish councils in South Staffordshire, each parish has their own chairman and clerk.
data.text:
Do you know an individual, group or organisation that deserves recognition for helping make South Staffordshire an amazing place to live in, work and visit?

Nominate them for one of the nine awards being presented at our upcoming invite-only awards ceremony in celebration of 50 years of South Staffordshire Council.

Please submit your nominations using the 'more information' link below before the extended deadline of 5pm on Friday 13th September.
